    matrixProcess.Rd

    A data frame produced by the function map_word_to_step

    Usage

    matrixProcess

    Format

    A data frame contains 67 variables

    degree

    the number of the steps used in a article.

    -1 means the input of Species name. 1 means the output of Species name.
